title: Somali Music 2
description:
Iska waran Salut Hi!


For info about this compilation, check out 'Somali Music 1':
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/4725927/Somali_Music_1


* * * * *


Second compilation of these sweet african tunes. Artists like Gulled Ahmed, Nimco Yasin, Mohamed Qooma, Nuur Eebe, Lafoole, AJ Abdiqadir Djibouti...

Some tracks are from the nr1 but with (a little bit) better sound quality this time.
The song Waaba or Doqoni hadal madeeysee (?) with Baastow is from one of the few cassettes I bought in Djibouti, a long time ago. I still love it!
 
97 songs, more than 9 hours of Somali music so... ENJOY nr2! :)


/F
